{"tid":1002388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國於南海囤積武器物資 美參議員：像準備第三次世界大戰","createTime":"2019-01-31T01:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T02:09:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"430b990f368ee95e0370b85b644a9f575bd06e47","tid":1002388,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:50:46.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3857/d3857288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3857%2Fd3857288.jpg&h=c1123a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美參議員認為，解放軍在南海的軍事部署像是為了第三次世界大戰準備。圖為中方實際控制的永暑礁。（圖／翻攝自軍報記者微博）<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 談中國在南海「堆武器囤物資」　美參議員：像準備第三次世界大戰 | ETtoday國際 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190130/1369947.htm#ixzz5e96Y4hob\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190130%2F1369947.htm%23ixzz5e96Y4hob&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6jsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=a3888ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190130/1369947.htm#ixzz5e96Y4hob</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook<br />\n面對中俄軍事擴張，美國聯邦參議院軍事委員會主席、共和黨籍參議員殷霍夫（James Inhofe）29日表示，中國在南海的軍事部署「像準備打第三次世界大戰」。殷霍夫說，美國必須向盟友溝通，確認一旦發生變故，會選擇哪一邊站。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國《海軍時報》（Navy Times）報導，參院情報委員會29日舉行聽證會，內容針對中國與俄國近年來的軍事擴張，以及如何讓人們更加理解此對世界秩序的威脅。殷霍夫表示，美方大量觀察到，中國在珊瑚礁與島嶼上建築防禦工事，在島礁上堆滿武器和儲備物資。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，北京近年不斷在南沙群島上擴張，激怒鄰近國家並挑戰國際法，美國也海軍進行常規「自由航行行動」（FONOPs.）。去年秋季，一艘中方軍艦逼近美國飛彈驅逐艦狄卡特號，差點發生碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n殷霍夫說，「看起來就像在準備第三次世界大戰」。他說，美方必須向南海周邊的盟友溝通，確認他們會「站在哪一邊」。另一方面，參議員與專家們認為，中國對美國與當今世界秩序的威脅，可能沒有完全被公眾瞭解。<br />\n<br />\n殷霍夫又說，自從二戰以來，美國人擁有某種樂觀的態度，認為美國擁有最好的一切。殷霍夫警告，「隨著1945年戰勝日本以及1991年蘇聯瓦解，美國在太平洋不容挑戰的軍事霸主地位已經不復存在。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 中國在南海「堆武器囤物資」美參議員：像準備第三次世界大戰 | ETtoday國際 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190130/1369947.htm#ixzz5e96Ilm00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190130%2F1369947.htm%23ixzz5e96Ilm00&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6jsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=18a3f0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190130/1369947.htm#ixzz5e96Ilm00</a>"},{"pid":"795328585ba87fb58a4de9e1a9935c41dab76825","tid":1002388,"uid":137157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"Bf4 paracel storm"},{"pid":"8d66e9a006f8200ae523d1cd2f32445f47bfe198","tid":1002388,"uid":61751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:58:14.000Z","msg":"你哋打啦 好悶呀.jpg"},{"pid":"8aae382df5ddce719169a29d8517d4bb21b01c0a","tid":1002388,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0de48bdad80ddde7a98b6dcb87cbc85d64f8050","tid":1002388,"uid":134215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"2nd Pacific War <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c55b63375cbb21eeb95bdf00f48680d174cfe40","tid":1002388,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0de48bdad80ddde7a98b6dcb87cbc85d64f8050","tid":1002388,"uid":134215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"2nd Pacific War <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"日本可以係太平洋打3，4年<br />\n<br />\n中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9080cb691c2037fe4ae41b357869d059c6de8f70","tid":1002388,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"嘩嘩嘩，大家有得走好走，香港一定陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /